@subsubheading Object State Interface

@samp{iGeneralMeshState} is the @sc{scf} interface that you can
use to set/get settings for a genmesh object. The definition of this
interface can be found in @file{CS/include/imesh/genmesh.h} and that's also the
include file you need to include in your applications to use this plugin.
Using this interface you can access the material, blending mode (mixmode),
and various other configuration parameters for a genmesh object.

